729819f-a.text:
(1)
3S12 Victory Boulevard, east side, between Baron Boulevard and Ridgeway Avenue (south of Travis Avenue). Butler's 1853 map designates this old house as a schoolhouse. On the 1899 and 1907
maps it appears as the property of Ridgeway.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
(2)
Another view of the o ld school house and adjoining dwellings,
looking north.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
